node.text:
“Find motivation in others success.” - @chancewho 
Years ago coming up in NZ I have fallen prey to the green eyed monster (envy). But then I questioned myself as to why I felt that way about someone’s success. I discovered it was learnt behavior, so once I identified the monster…I was able to kill it! Till this day when I see someone thriving in anything be it financially, emotionally, physically…etc I find inspiration and motivation from that. If you’re reading this and you feel a way about me shinning, this ain’t about you.
But if the show fits… 👠
#wedonthatewemotivate 🦖

node.text:
✨🥝
Thank you to everyone worldwide for the love with TeKilla Kiwi.  Available everywhere soon, I promise!  In the meantime and if you are in the USandA (Borat voice), make sure you go to the link in my bio to enter the raffle to support @seedsofchangefoundation and try your chance to win a year’s supply of clean energy drinks courtesy of @KillCliff, $500 worth of fuel courtesy of @GetBiofuel, and two tickets to my next fight!

node.text:
🚨🚨🚨🚨🚨
-Super pumped to launch my own energy drink with Kill Cliff. TeKilla Kiwi!! ✨🥝

-Get yours while you can at killcliff.com, they will sell out quick!
-the best tasting and most refreshing clean energy drink. 📠
